title: Looking for Plat+ 10 mans
body:
Looking for some friendly 10 mans to destroy my ego a little.
Typical silver player attitude where i think i can roll with the big boys but obviously can't cause I just think Im in elo hell.
Just seeing where I am at and want to try and learn off some more experienced players.
If anyone knows anywhere where i can get 10 mans against better players would be much appreciated!

JG Main, with a strong Mid lane too.
OP.GG = http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=jebby

Thanks everyone!
